content: There are certain people you meet along your path in life that leave a lasting impression. For me, Sukanya Krishnan has been one of them. On a professional level she is tops. Her ability to navigate through a breaking news story is unsurpassed. She can speak off the cuff about any topic from politics and international news to fashion and entertainment. Her knowledge of every borough and stitch of New York City proves her love for the place she calls home. She takes her role of being the voice of the people seriously, always willing to stop and speak with everyone she meets on the street. On a personal level, she is loyal, giving, and has the biggest heart. Through the ups and down in life, she has been there to lend an ear or a shoulder to cry on. She is a dedicated mother, wife and friend who most of all is REAL. What you see is what you get. I look forward to many more years of friendship, and learning where her journey takes her next. ‚ù§Ô∏è
name: Lisa Mateo
